    <p class="s1" style="padding-top: 3pt;padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">COMBINED THIRD PARTY
        LIABILITY LIMIT <span style=" color: #000;">K200,000.00</span></p>
    <p style="padding-top: 8pt;padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Bodily injury/death Property damage
    </p>
    <p style="padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 14pt;text-align: left;">Passenger Liability (authorised
        and unauthorised)</p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p class="s1" style="padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">EXCESS</p>
    <p style="padding-top: 8pt;padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">10% minimum K500 each claim for
        third party property damage</p>
    <p class="s3" style="padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Addition to own damage excess</p>
    <p style="padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">10% minimum K500 each claim for young drivers (less
        than 25 years old)</p>
    <p style="padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">10% minimum K500 each claim for inexperienced
        drivers (holder of a valid driver’s license for less than 2 years)</p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p class="s1" style="padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">PREMIUM CALCULATION</p>
