    <p class="s1" style="padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Plus 5% Levy ZMW 12.57</p>
    <p class="s1" style="padding-left: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Total Premium Due ZMW 264</p>
